headline: Defense stocks offer attractive value heading into 2026, Morgan Stanley says
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley sees U.S. defense stocks as attractive going into 2026, arguing that valuations fail to reflect continued growth in the U.S. defense budget despite political uncertainty.
